---
title: Chicken Korma Style Curry with broccoli and rice
description: If you're a fan of curry—but not a fan of spice—then you're in luck. This chicken korma curry has only the faintest hint of heat, but that definitely doesn't mean it's lacking in flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R02_W05_IE_IEXCC0099-2__KB_Main_high-f52b0409.jpg
